description: Trader Vic's tart Jamaican grog with passion fruit, pineapple, and a hard shake over double rocks.
author: Victor "Trader Vic" Bergeron (1940s, Trader Vic's)
adapted_by: Beachbum Berry
year: 1940s
venue: Trader Vic's, Oakland
