---

In a #shaker{} combine @dark Jamaican rum{2%oz}, @passion fruit syrup{1%oz}, @pineapple juice{1%oz}, @fresh lemon juice{1%oz}, and @Angostura bitters{1%dash} with @cracked ice{1%cup}.
Shake well.
Pour unstrained into a short #double old-fashioned glass{}.
Garnish with a @lime wedge{1} and a @brandied cherry{1} on a pick.
